%F A197032 x = 2 + tan phi where 1 + 2 tan phi = 1/(sin phi + cos phi), whence x = 1 + A357469 = the only real root of x^3 - 4*x^2 + 6*x - 5. - _M. F. Hasler_, Nov 08 2022
